<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_23_r1l13"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . Als vns ewr gnade nehſt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von ſach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l14">vvegen antreffende <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> Juden Joſſe . Vnd Joheln 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Jm </del> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Juden etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l16"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> . Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> darauff </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_23_r1l15">darümb </ab></add> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dyener <expan>Burkh<ex>art</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l18">Reickerſhofer cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden geſant . der vns 
<add><ab facs="#facs_23_r1l17">wıder </ab></add> geſagt hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l19">vvie Er <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> handel als ſich der bey vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>loffen</expan> hat / <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l20">gnaden wol ercʒelt vnd fürbraht hab . als 
<del rend="strikethrough">dar </del> der <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> an vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l21">kumen iſt . Aber vvie darümb . 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſo </del> dewht <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade . daʒ der <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l22">Johel Jude . oder aber der JudenRate bey vns icht anders getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l23">heten <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> bıllich wer . So vvöllet / <expan>yemand<ex>en</ex></expan> der ewrn in einer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l25">kürcʒe darümb hercʒu vns ſchicken . 
<add><ab facs="#facs_23_r1l24">die ſache </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> So <expan>vvolle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir darümb rede </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l26">
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd wıderrede </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_23_line_1577008088138_478">cʒu </ab></add> verhören / VVer <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Juden 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>dhein<ex>er</ex></expan></del> icht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l27">vnbillichs getan <expan>hete<ex>n</ex></expan> Darcʒu wöllten vvir durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> tun </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l30">
<add><ab facs="#facs_23_line_1577008241937_586">daʒ vvir hofften </ab></add> daʒ 
<add><ab facs="#facs_23_r1l28">ewr gnade vernemen ſolt daʒ vns ſolch ſach niht lıeb wer </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vvir hoffen Jr wol verſteen vvir hofften <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden cʒu <expan>gefalle<ex>n</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l32">
<add><ab facs="#facs_23_r1l31">vnd getrawen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> wol Jr wollet das alſo vmb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> tun Möcht </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Möcht aber des niht geſein des vvir doch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> nıht <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_line_1577008167284_537">
<add><ab facs="#facs_23_line_1577008244174_591">aber des niht geſein </ab><ab facs="#facs_23_line_1577008246731_596">het <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> der <expan>obgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_23_line_1577008249964_601"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> Jude Joſſe cʒu </ab><ab facs="#facs_23_line_1577008252697_606"><expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> Johell </ab><ab facs="#facs_23_line_1577008256071_611"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> aber cʒu <expan>dheine<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_23_line_1577008259804_616"><expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Juden </ab><ab facs="#facs_23_line_1577008262958_621">
<del rend="strikethrough">hie </del> icht <expan>cʒeſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_23_line_1577008265848_626">darümb </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> So </del> <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir dem 
<add><ab facs="#facs_23_r1l34"><expan>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> Joſſe </del> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> Judem Joſſe 
<add><ab facs="#facs_23_r1l36">oder aber <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> von dem obgen </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l40">
<add><ab facs="#facs_23_r1l38"><expan>ſcheinpote<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt hie vor des Reıchs Rıchter </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Johell oder aber cʒu <expan>dheine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jude <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Juden hie bey vns </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l42">
<del rend="strikethrough">icht cʒuſp </del> <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogens</expan> ſleunigs rehten <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen <expan>vvenn</expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l45">des ermandt werden So <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>e</expan> Juden anheim vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_line_1577008192354_554">dievveil ſıe die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſind . 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Vnd <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> wol </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_line_1577008207921_568"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dinſt beweıſen möhten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l52">des wern etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l53"><expan>vvılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> Mendel et </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_23_r1l54"><expan>St<ex>efan</ex></expan> Coler <expan>p<ex>er</ex></expan> ſe </ab>
